WEBVTT

00:13:59.441 --> 00:14:02.529
wife-beating, gay-bashing ancestors?

00:14:02.529 --> 00:14:05.321
SP: I'm sure everyone here
could think of an example.

00:14:05.321 --> 00:14:07.351
RNG: I opt for the mistreatment of animals

00:14:07.351 --> 00:14:09.062
in factory farms.

00:14:09.062 --> 00:14:11.292
SP: The imprisonment of nonviolent drug offenders

00:14:11.292 --> 00:14:13.994
and the toleration of rape in our nation's prisons.

00:14:13.994 --> 00:14:16.719
RNG: Scrimping on donations to life-saving charities

00:14:16.719 --> 00:14:18.376
in the developing world.

00:14:18.376 --> 00:14:20.718
SP: The possession of nuclear weapons.

00:14:20.718 --> 00:14:23.095
RNG: The appeal to religion to justify

00:14:23.095 --> 00:14:24.735
the otherwise unjustifiable,

00:14:24.735 --> 00:14:27.247
such as the ban on contraception.

00:14:27.247 --> 00:14:29.035
SP: What about religious faith in general?

00:14:29.035 --> 00:14:31.216
RNG: Eh, I'm not holding my breath.